OL,3,CMother in stem cell donor plea to give
OL,4,Cyoung sons 'a chance at a normal life'
OL,6,FA mother has launched an urgent appeal
OL,7,Fto find stem cell donors for her two
OL,8,Fyoung sons in a bid to "give them a
OL,9,Fchance at a normal life".
OL,11,FCezar Nica, two, and David Nica, 10
OL,12,Fmonths, have been diagnosed with
OL,13,FWiskott-Aldrich Syndrome (WAS), a rare
OL,14,Fand life-threatening genetic disorder.
OL,16,FTheir mother, Marcela Zberea, 29, said
OL,17,Fthe boys currently lead "very
OL,18,Frestricted lives" and are too
OL,19,Fvulnerable to go to playgroups or
OL,20,Fspend time with other children.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@XO]yD@YOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
